#summary Golf Markup Language Documentation: simpleType MediaTypeEnum.

== Name ==

*[SMediaTypeEnum MediaTypeEnum]*

  	

===  Super Types ===
{{{
string
  |
  +--MediaTypeEnum (restriction)
}}}
----
    

===  Documentation ===
        
			List of values for types of media used in golfml.
		
  	
===  Properties ===

  	This component is not nillable.
---- 	
        
===  Model ===

	('photograph' | 'video' | 'hole-fly-over' | 'hole-presentation' | 'hole-yardage' | 'yardage-book' | 'course-map' | 'google-earth' | 'other')

----
    

===  Local Usage ===

    	[AMediaTypeAttributes MediaTypeAttributes]
----
    <xs:simpleType name="MediaTypeEnum">  <xs:restriction base="xs:string">    <xs:enumeration value="photograph"/>    <xs:enumeration value="video"/>    <xs:enumeration value="hole-fly-over"/>    <xs:enumeration value="hole-presentation"/>    <xs:enumeration value="hole-yardage"/>    <xs:enumeration value="yardage-book"/>    <xs:enumeration value="course-map"/>    <xs:enumeration value="google-earth"/>    <xs:enumeration value="other"/>  </xs:restriction></xs:simpleType>
----
